Third-party components

This repository bundles the CTP (Comprehensive Transaction Platform) C++
SDK from Shanghai Futures Information Technology Co., Ltd (SFIT) under
`v6.7.11_20250714_traderapi/`. The CTP SDK is the property of SFIT and is
distributed here for convenience only. It is governed by SFIT's own
license terms — refer to the SDK's accompanying documentation and the
SimNow site (http://www.simnow.com.cn/) for authoritative terms.

This repository fetches the SQLite amalgamation (sqlite.org), which is in
the public domain.

If `ENABLE_PYTHON=ON`, this repository links against pybind11 (BSD-3) and
the system Python installation.
